    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in peerless, showroom-floor condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that satisfies even the most discerning collector. Meticulously maintained and mechanically absolute, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade caliber.",
      "price": 43900.0,
